Packages that use net.ajaest.jdk.data.auxi
net.ajaest.jdk.core.main contains JavaDIKt's main classes (Launcher, Messages, GUIEngine,...)

net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict contains specific JavaDiKt's database management classes.

net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict.sort contains specific JavaDiKt's auxiliary classes for sorting API 
net.ajaest.jdk.data.kanji contains specific JavaDiKt's auxiliary classes for kanji type API 
net.ajaest.jdk.tools contains specific JavaDiKt's tools to build kanji database 
net.ajaest.jdk.tools.adders contains specific JavaDiKt's tools to append information to kanji database sources 
net.ajaest.jdk.tools.parsers contains specific JavaDiKt's tools to parse kanji information from files 
net.ajaest.jdk.tools.test.data.auxi contains specific JavaDiKt's net.ajaest.jdk.data.auxi test cases 
net.ajaest.jdk.tools.test.data.dict contains specific JavaDiKt's net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict test cases 
net.ajaest.lib.swing.util contains SWING components and tools
